title: Unemployment rate in Somalia 2019
summary: Overall Unemployment rate has increased over the Year.
Unemployment rate is slightly increasing from 2007 to 2009, roughly constant from 2009 to 2015, and finally slightly decreasing from 2015 to 2017.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2008 and 2009.
Maximum Unemployment rate, about 14.63 was reported at Year 2013
Minimum Unemployment rate about 13.69 was reached at Year 2008
min_summary: In general Unemployment rate has stayed the same over the Year.
Unemployment rate is slightly increasing from 2007 to 2009, roughly constant from 2009 to 2015, and finally slightly decreasing from 2015 to 2017.
